    "The discriminator, conversely, aims at correctly classifying real data as genuine and fake data as counterfeit.",
    "The adversarial competition in GAN training results in a dynamic equilibrium where the generator continually refines its ability to produce challenging data for discrimination 37.",
    "while the discriminator refines the ability to distinguish generated data from real training data.",
    "This equilibrium signifies successful GAN training.",
    "The trained generator can therefore be used to generate synthetic data to train the ML models 38."
  ],
